                <h2>FAQs</h2>
                <br/>
                <div class="copy copy-single">
                  <ol style="list-style: none;">
                    <li>
                      <strong>Which types of payments do you accept?</strong>
                      <p>All major credit cards, PayPal, checks, and wire transfer.</p>
